<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>28</hymn_number>
<title>ZANLEI THANGTHATNAK CH28</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Tlang in ni a liam riangmang, Van nih lei kha a tongh cang, Van ah
 khin arfi hna cu, Mei inn bang an ceu lioah, Hngak law bia tuah.

[C1]
   Thiang bik, Thiang bik, Thiang bik, Bawipa Pathian! Van le lei ah na
   khat dih, An in lawmh, Van le lei nih, Maw sang bik Bawi.

[V2]
 Nunnak Bawi van kulh chungah, Nangmah huhphenhnak inn ah Nangmah an
 kawlmi kan khawm, Na thladem tangin kan pom, Kan umpi ko.

[C2]
   Thiang bik, Thiang bik, Thiang bik, Bawipa Pathian! Van le lei ah na
   khat dih, An in lawmh, Van le lei nih, Maw sang bik Bawi.

[V3]
 Muih thlam aa zelh lioah khan, Dawt thinlung nih a kulh dih, Sunpar
 arfi lengah khin, Na hmai hmuh kan duh ca-ah, Kan lung an zuang.

[C3]
   Thiang bik, Thiang bik, Thiang bik, Bawipa Pathian! Van le lei ah na
   khat dih, An in lawmh, Van le lei nih, Maw sang bik Bawi.

[V4]
 Zan fikceu a liam tikah, Chun le zan an liam zongah, Vanmi Bawipa, na
 thawngin, Zing khuaceu a ra than i, Muihnak a dih.

[C4]
   Thiang bik, Thiang bik, Thiang bik, Bawipa Pathian! Van le lei ah na
   khat dih, An in lawmh, Van le lei nih, Maw sang bik Bawi.</lyrics>
<key>Ab</key>
</song>